nodes.notes:
Extracts the new Salesmate contact ID and carries all lead data forward to the dashboard step.

The contact ID is logged in your Google Sheet so you can jump from any dashboard row directly to the contact in Salesmate: https://yourfirm.salesmate.io/contacts/{id}

If the Salesmate step failed, salesmate_contact_id will be empty. The lead is still logged in the dashboard and you can add the ID manually later.

